Requirements:
node.js
libnotify notify-send (Linux Gnome)
growl (Mac OSX)
node.js growl package (Mac OSX)
compass (SCSS compiler)
php-cli (PHP lint)

Parameters:
--check-js			Check .js files with Crockford's JSLint 
--check-php			Check .php files for parse errors
--compass			Check and compile .sass and .scss files with compass (requires that webhelper was started in the directory where config.rb resides)
--verbose			Print output to the terminal
--ubuntu			Print output with notify-send
--growl				Print output with growl
--no-check-on-add	Do not check files when they are
